TITAN

Titans are the most balanced of the giant races, combining exceptional
Physical Strength with respectable intelligence and mental fortitude.
They are the best candidates for demanding OCCs among giant races.

ATTRIBUTES (approximate ranges):
  IQ: 5-20   ME: 5-20   MA: 5-20   PS: 15-40 (Supernatural)
  PP: 3-18   PE: 12-32  PB: 4-14   Spd: 7-22

DAMAGE POOL:
  SDC: 4d6 x10 (approx 40-240)

SPECIAL ABILITIES:
  - Supernatural Physical Strength and Endurance
  - Enhanced IQ, ME, and MA for a giant
  - Giant size combat advantage

PENALTIES:
  - Giant size limitations
  - D-Bee status in Coalition territory

OCC ELIGIBLE: Yes.
ALIGNMENT: Any.

See also: algor frost giant, jotan, nimro fire giant, races
